steps.description:
Fix the check_captures_constraint_traces test in crates/reify-eval/tests/boundary5_engine.rs to add the missing c2_node assertion. The comment on line 102 claims 'thickness should be depended on by volume, c0, c1, c2' but c2 is never asserted. Constraint c2 is `hole_diameter < thickness * 2` (from bracket_compiled_module fixture at constraint index 2) which reads thickness. Add:
  let c2_node = NodeId::Constraint(ConstraintNodeId::new("Bracket", 2));
  assert!(thickness_deps.contains(&c2_node));
after the existing c1_node assertion on line 108.
